divs: Sighting DetailsWhile walking home from the neighbors, I saw a HUGE object flying overhead blocking view of stars with no sound, it passed by more than 10 times faster than any airplane, plus the size was enormous. There was no sound, and it was black, I could not see any shape either. If I had not been looking at the bright stars I would of never known it passed by.
